  <brief_title>Infant-parent Skin-to-skin Contact During Screening for Retinopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is There a Difference in Pain Score, Stress Response and Motor Repertoire in Infants Given Skin-to-skin Contact With the Mother/Father or Standard Care During Screening for Retinopathy?</official_title>
